<div id='header-inner'>
<div class='titlewrapper'>
<h1 class='title'>
<a href='http://tooloftrade.blogspot.com/'>The tools of the trade</a>
</h1>
</div>
<div class='descriptionwrapper'>
<p class='description'><span>My name is Martin H. Skjelvareid, and I am a developer and researcher in acoustics and signal processing. In this blog I'll publish various posts on the tools I use in my everyday work. I have been using Matlab and LaTeX for some years now, and I am also in the middle of a (neverending?) learning process on Linux. This blog is a place for me to collect my tips and tricks, and hopefully also a place for others to find useful information. Feel free to comment! :-)</span></p>
</div>
</div>
</div></div>
</div>
